snippet.title: Golden Sun: Dark Dawn (DS) E3 2010 Trailer
snippet.description: Nintendo Life - Nintendo shows off the newest trailer of its upcoming epic RPG, Golden Sun: Dark Dawn, heading to DS in holiday 2010.
